data.description: Discover the charm of this North Knoxville ranch-style home, providing 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms in a conveniently located neighborhood near shopping, dining, and parks. Both owners and guests alike will surely appreciate the inviting design, featuring a breakfast bar in the kitchen and a generously sized family room. All matching stainless appliances are included. The garage has been creatively converted into an additional room, perfect for an office or storage. Abundant natural light fills the space. Step outside to find a roomy deck and an expansive backyard surrounded by a wooden privacy fence. Your ideal home is ready for you!
